        OK from what I was told by a good friend of mine , who was in zone when this started, it's a plague from Bertox . He says there was a zone wide message saying that Bertox the god had trapped/enslaved/imprisoned gods to &nbsp;his plane (of Disease)  <br> Now the theory going about higher up &nbsp;is that since most GMs themselves are going to nk and &nbsp;do not know &nbsp;whats going on, meaning it's some VI &nbsp;event and not &nbsp;a GM event, that perhaps VI are about to open a new planes called (maybe) Plane of Disease. /shrug <br> <br>Sounds possible but who really knows.All I know is that &nbsp;any GM's I spoke to say they dont know whats happening and &nbsp;they then port into NK to see for themselves lol. <br> <br>I got me 51st Warrior ready to go at a moments notice no matter what happens lol.

