        -- Posted by Talanye on 7:36 pm on April 17, 2001<p>
        Hail and well met all, <br> &nbsp; Well, I have read as much as I can about this plague on the plains of Karana, and it seems there is more going on then just this plague. &nbsp;It seems that on some servers, that Firionia Vie, as well as Innorak's daughter has been spoted, and lots of unusual events are taking place in the lands of Norrath. <br> &nbsp; The plague of Karana started as this: <br>Mordavin Telase, husband of Azibelle Spavin was hung by (under orders from) Antonius Bayle for conspiracy. &nbsp;Apparently Mordavin was conducting research for Bertoxx (the god of plagues), as well. &nbsp;Well, Azibelle got a bunch of people together and did a ceremony and called on Bertoxx to come to the Karana's. &nbsp;He did. &nbsp;He announced things to the whole zone about how he was going to "bless the land" with three things, the green mist that comes during the rains, the rabid animails, and the swarmlings (who sometimes spawn with a Mother, who cons red to a level 30), and the Karanas have never been the same since. &nbsp;If you talk with the farmers in the Karana's, they will tell you this story. <br> &nbsp; i suggest that if you are interested in finding out more, to check out this website. &nbsp;www.1fol.cjb.net &nbsp;on their message boards there is a board called &nbsp;(something like) We are at WAR and HERE is all the Info. &nbsp;Warning, it is VERY long, and indepth...lots about the details of the History of the lands of Norrath. &nbsp;There are over 13 pages of posts there, so make sure you have some time to read them. <br> &nbsp;Anyway, hope that helps a bit! &nbsp;

